1.0.0 (2026-06-12)
------------------

- Initial release
- GsniItem for creating StatusNotifierItem tray icons
- GsniHost and GsniHostItem for consuming SNI items
- DBusMenu (com.canonical.dbusmenu) server adapter
- GIO native menu export (org.gtk.Menus / org.gtk.Actions)
- D-Bus watcher lifecycle management with auto-reconnect
- GdkPixbuf to D-Bus a(iiay) serialization
- GObject Introspection with Python bindings
- GTK4 system tray host example
- RPM and DEB packaging
- PyPI distribution via meson-python
